{
  "stem": "4700.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, it upset me a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I feel we are the last ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have to bear witness, if-- you get all sorts of stupid questions when you're there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People think that the photographs are posed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they don't-- we say-- well, I say to people, it's the German, from the German archives.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say, why would they take photographs like that?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, because they were enjoyable activities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They enjoyed shooting the Jews, so they took photographs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was in the German archives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's, it's all genuine, from the German archives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There are statistics, there are even train time tables to, to the various extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it says that the wagons are not to stop on the way in these and these stops, but go directly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the weight is so much loaded, and so much empty.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, it's all there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's all there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We get a lot of schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that is--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To hear because lots of the children, A, never met a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And B, never, ever saw a Holocaust survivor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember when my uncles talked about World War I, I thought it's old hat, and that was 20 years later.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or not even that. 15 years later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thought it was old hat, and who wants to listen to it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, I mean, it's similar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a long time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it's about-- I think I'd just like to say I'm very grateful to be in Australia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think the people here were very friendly and really welcomed us with open arms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And I felt-- after the war, I felt a certain anti-Semitism, even in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
